title: Trade deadline proposals & TNF preview
itunes:title: Trade deadline proposals & TNF preview
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – break down all the news from around the NFL including the Broncos 27-9 victory over the Texans on Monday night, and running back Arian Foster’s retirement from football. Then, the heroes throw out a few trade proposals they’d like to see happen before next week’s deadline, and preview the Thursday night matchup between the Jaguars and the Titans.
